precis:
Enactment of the G8 SUMMIT PRIVILEGES AND IMMUNITIES ORDER, 2002 - which
grants certain of the privileges and immunities set out in the Convention
on the Privileges and Immunities of the United Nations to people attending
the G8 Summit (2002) in Kananaskis or the preparatory meetings to be held
in Whistler and Halifax.
